parameters:
Dynamite Abalone: Wabi~... To think that I, of all people,
would be defeated by such small fries... I lost to the
mayor, and even to the Shark Duke... It seems the time has
come for me to retire...

Memimi: You were strong, Dynamite Abalone, but you lacked
conviction... The one who wins in the end is the one who
keeps a strong heart and never gives up. Take this chance to
change your heart and work for the sake of those without
power...

Bunny-chan: I won't forgive you for a while, you know~! This
guy is going to become a volunteer staff member for the
Monster Fight! You absolutely must obey my orders! Ei!

Dynamite Abalone: Ugyaaaahhh!!! Huh, this might feel a bit
good... Maybe working for others isn't so bad after all...
Memimi: That's not quite what I meant...

Brachiocondor: I've been a monster for a long time, but...
this is the first time I've seen such a grotesque form. It
was my suggestion, but I wonder if we've created something
terrible...

Memimi: No matter what form I take, I remain myself. For the
future of Dorotoku City, I'm willing to become a monster...

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan, you look so cool! Let's take a
photo together♪
Memimi: Oh, take one with my smartphone too! Yay!

Bunny-chan: This is super good, Memimi-chaaan! Can I upload
this to SNS? It's totally going to go viral!

Memimi: Eh? No... I mean, about SNS, Bunny-chan's account
is...

Bunny-chan: ...I forgot about that, what to do... Well, it's
fine, I won't be defeated by something like this!! Just like
Memimi-chan, I won't get discouraged!

??? : "There's probably no monster on Earth that can defeat
you now... The time has come to settle our wretched past
with Doride City... I'm counting on you... my Shark Head,
please make good use of it..."

Memimi: "Since there are no spare monster suits for the
great boss, they're all quite worn out... I will definitely
defeat the mayor and have them sewn up for you, so please
wait just a little longer..."

Memimi: (Anomalocaris is looking at his smartphone with an
unusually serious expression... He also has many
subordinates and carries a lot of responsibility... Maybe
the prolonged lack of communication has been causing trouble
in various places...)

Anomalocaris: ...Hmm! This one's worth saving... The image
quality is high... The picture below looks good too...
Save...

Anomalocaris: Oh... Ohhh! Bunny-chan... I absolutely must
secure this one... I'll tweet and bookmark it as well...

Memimi: What are you doing with such a serious face, you
pervert!!!

Cerburus Octopus: Ugh... Even though I'm restrained, the
Dynamite Abalone is seriously scary... Defeat the mayor
quickly and come back...

Memimi: He probably has no will to fight left... Don't be so
scared. In any case, I don't plan on dragging out the
battle.

Cerburus Octopus: (The Dynamite Abalone is the scariest
thing, but I wish I could calm down and masturbate as soon
as possible... With her and Bunny-chan providing such high-
quality fap material in abundance... I can't hold it in
anymore...)

Memimi: (He must be tired from being in a state of extreme
tension for so long... I must settle this quickly...)

Underling: To combine the suits of the strongest monsters in
the city into one...! It's as if you've embodied our ideal
of unifying the city!!

Memimi: If everyone's feelings become one, there's nothing
to fear, no matter the situation. No matter how powerful the
mayor may be, we have inherited the power of many
monsters...

Underling: To think we'd actually defeat Dynamite
Abalone...! This is seriously intense, maybe, just maybe!!
One unbelievable thing after another keeps happening, and I
can't contain my excitement...

Memimi: Hehehe, you should look forward to it... I'm about
to knock out the mayor with a single punch and show you an
even more astonishing sight.

Underling: I never thought I'd see Bunny-chan's bare breasts
in my lifetime, but there they were... At this point,
nothing would surprise me. What in the world is going to
happen next...
Memimi: I'm going to punch you...

Underling: Do your best in the final battle... I really wish
I could go with you to support you...

Memimi: If we walk in a crowd, we'll stand out, and if it
turns into a brawl, there will be more injuries... It's best
for me to go alone and settle things with the mayor one-on-
one. He has his pride too, so he probably won't stoop to
ganging up and lynching just me.

Underling: Even if they don't lynch you, there's a high
chance they'll gang-rape you... Bunny-chan was just recently
violated by all the monsters in the underground city...
Memimi: Stop it! Don't say that!!

Bunny-chan: I'm still pretty shocked by it, so can we please
not talk about that...
